  "topic": "Sigma and Pi Bonds",
  "question": "How many \u03c3 and \u03c0 bonds in C\u2082H\u2084?",
  "options": {
    "A": "3\u03c3, 1\u03c0",
    "B": "5\u03c3, 1\u03c0",
    "C": "5\u03c3, 2\u03c0",
    "D": "6\u03c3, 1\u03c0"
  },
  "answer": "B",
  "explanation": "C\u2082H\u2084: 1 C=C (1\u03c3 + 1\u03c0) + 4 C-H bonds (4\u03c3) = 5\u03c3 and 1\u03c0 bonds."
